{"tid":543021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙重標準】浸大強國學生當街做愛毋需停學處分  香港學生爆粗要無限期停學至另行通知","createTime":"2018-01-28T05:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:00.000Z","uid":136994,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc6231cce83cdfbfed2366c6938612d9d116064","tid":543021,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180128/57761632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57761632&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJ8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1f675f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57761632&h=1f32a362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180128/57761632</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517058184_5de1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517058184_5de1.jpg&h=ea3d5ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸大學生反普通話畢業標準風波持續，兩名牽頭「佔領」語文中心的學生因被指對教職員言行不當，遭勒令即時停學。浸大生前日就發起校內集會遊行，向校方表達不滿，其中有要求撤回對兩名學生的處分等。「反普考試」因facebook群組「浸大山神」而起，但由網上掀起的浸大風波豈止於此。Facebook群組「放棄治療院」前日分享了《蘋果》2年多前的新聞，當時有一對內地來港的大學生情侶在街頭「打野戰」，帖中笑言「當年咁X樣都未洗停學啦！同學！因為佢講普通話嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n當年兩名內地生街頭「打野戰」的小風波，兩名主角分別為19歲的浸大男生及一名理大女生，有指兩人將馬路當大床纏綿了45分鐘，直至警方到場大喝才醒來。由於兩人在公眾地方行為不檢，被法官判處社會服務令。「放棄治療院」發帖網民認為，當年學生在大街上激戰亦不至於處即時停學，指是因為該事主「講普通話嘛...殖民地黎架！ 講好普通話係必需架！仲有特權架」，質疑校方在兩事上做法不公、雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，浸會大學即時停學處分所引校規已多年沒用；有指，若學生所牽涉事件一經進入法律程序，校方一般不會再作「停學處分」，以免涉事學生遭重複被罰。"},{"pid":"baf9345a6ffb063a6e2b25f9ad073b328d3a0da6","tid":543021,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"係恰鳩你呀 吹咩<br />\n夠薑武裝革命丫"},{"pid":"32d02dac5c4de47e5dcb76e93e645f2db8afc531","tid":543021,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"王敦倫"},{"pid":"2b3d2a096e491e81fdaf4d44183e39a640c85b63","tid":543021,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf9345a6ffb063a6e2b25f9ad073b328d3a0da6","tid":543021,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"係恰鳩你呀 吹咩<br />\n夠薑武裝革命丫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6623e7e2a0f0303a068740881c6b79260db45bc1","tid":543021,"uid":36104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:26:26.000Z","msg":"當然雙重標準啦<br />\n蝗係中國公民<br />\n香港人係壓榨對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d65bd478e29e125e3858a2569fe112801ba2f3","tid":543021,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}